data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought after Browns Valley neighborhood! This stunning residence offers everything you've been looking for, with its spacious layout, modern updates, and captivating features. With 5 bedrooms and 3 full baths spread across two levels, there is ample space for your growing family or hosting guests.  As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the tasteful upgrades, including modern floors and fresh paint. The heart of this home is the open kitchen and inviting pool, perfect for cooling off during those warm summer days or entertaining family and friends. The expansive private yard provides a sanctuary of relaxation and fun, with plenty of room for outdoor activities or RV.  This property boasts a 3-car garage with additional storage, ensuring you have ample room for your vehicles and belongings. You'll enjoy the convenience of nearby amenities, including top-rated schools, shopping centers, and parks, all within a short distance. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a home that combines modern comforts with an ideal location. Schedule your private tour today and make this magnificent residence your own!
